        public ParserGroupBuilder(PropertyStore propertyStore)
        Create an empty parser group using the specified property store for settings.

        Note: Modifying the specified property store externally will also modify it here.

        Parameters:
        propertyStore - The property store containing all settings common to all parsers in this group.

      • classLoader

        public ParserGroupBuilder classLoader(ClassLoader classLoader)
        Specifies the classloader to use when resolving classes from strings for all parsers in this group.

        Can be used for resolving class names when the classes being created are in a different classloader from the Juneau code.

        If null, the system classloader will be used to resolve classes.

        Parameters:
        classLoader - The new classloader.
        Returns:
        This object (for method chaining).
        See Also:
        PropertyStore.setClassLoader(ClassLoader)
